chiving, Deduplication and Quantum products. With a strong project manager and a flexible delivery team, I would recommend Kanatek as a company that has an excellent professional services staff.[/blockquote][blockquote]Kanatek''s backup and recovery managed services team provides Nortel with the needed resources and tools to ensure the availability of our data through cost-effective solutions and unparalleled support. Data is everything and Kanatek helps us ensure the availability of our valuable resources. You can rebuild the network or rebuild a server, but you cannot rebuild your data if you lose it.[/blockquote][blockquote align="pull-right"]I would like to compliment Kanatek for their service support. CIBC Mellon holds extremely high standards for vendors and Kanatek has consistently exceeded expectations in their proactive preparation, knowledge and response time. The Kanatek team has been attentive, patient, and committed to forging a strong partnership with our organization. I am confident that we can build on this relationship and look forward to continuing to work with Kanatek.[/blockquote][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]Partners[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-24 20:54:15', '2015-01-24 20:54:15', '', 4, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/01/24/4-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
