(63, 1, '2015-01-24 21:23:45', '2015-01-24 21:23:45', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Why we [text_color color]standout[/text_color] in a crowd</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>A Message from the Kanatek Leadership Team</h3>\r\nDear Colleagues, Clients, and Friends,\r\n\r\nKanatek has been in business for over 30 years and we have built our reputation on trust, quality, and our expertise in the IT field.  We have evolved from a three-person staff building mainframe computers into a successful enterprise of dedicated and brilliant data storage professionals.\r\n\r\nIt is our belief that corporate evolution is necessary to stay in the game and once again, we are evolving to reflect the changing needs of our clients and their businesses.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Our Mission</h3>\r\nKanatek''s mission is to provide our clients with specialized services for safeguarding, managing, and supporting their data infrastructure.  We understand how important your data is to your business and we are here to provide our subject matter expertise.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Our Values</h3>\r\nWe have been fortunate enough to hold a longevity that is rare in this business and it is our belief that our corporate values and people can be attributed to this success.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Our Corporate Values</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="infinity2" icon_color="#fff"]Enduring[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe have built a reputation of dependable performance since 1982.\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading 