(78, 1, '2015-01-25 04:10:55', '2015-01-25 04:10:55', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Why we [text_color color]standout[/text_color] in a crowd</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>A Message from the Kanatek Leadership Team</h3>\r\nDear Colleagues, Clients, and Friends,\r\n\r\nKanatek has been in business for over 30 years and we have built our reputation on trust, quality, and our expertise in the IT field.  We have evolved from a three-person staff building mainframe computers into a successful enterprise of dedicated and brilliant data storage professionals.\r\n\r\nIt is our belief that corporate evolution is necessary to stay in the game and once again, we are evolving to reflect the changing needs of our clients and their businesses.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Our Mission</h3>\r\nKanatek''s mission is to provide our clients with specialized services for safeguarding, managing, and supporting their data infrastructure.  We understand how important your data is to your business and we are here to provide our subject matter expertise.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Our Values</h3>\r\nWe have been fortunate enough to hold a longevity that is rare in this business and it is our belief that our corporate values and people can be attributed to this success.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Our Corporate Values</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="infinity2" icon_color="#fff"]Enduring[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe have built a reputation of dependable performance since 1982.\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="megaphone5" icon_color="#fff"]Flexible[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe listen and respond quickly to our clients'' needs.\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="focus" icon_color="#fff"]Focused[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe are focused on delivering value in everything we do.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="spell-check" icon_color="#fff"]Ethical[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe fulfill our promises with care, honesty, and respect.\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="tools" icon_color="#fff"]Creative[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe use imagination and originality to serve our clients.\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="heart6" icon_color="#fff"]Trusted[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe forge lasting relationships with our clients and partners.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">The Team</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=""]\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="group2" icon_color="#fff"]Principles[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="" post="" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n<h5>Peter Karneef</h5>\r\n<h6>Chief Executive Officer</h6>\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="" post="" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n<h5>Terry Kell</h5>\r\n<h6>President</h6>\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text css_animation=""]\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="group2" icon_color="#fff"]Management[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="" post="" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n<h5>Brad Beckett</h5>\r\n<h6>Vice President of Sales and Marketing</h6>\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="" post="" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n<h5>Darryl Levesque</h5>\r\n<h6>Director of Technology Solutions</h6>\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="" post="" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n<h5>Michael De Cesare</h5>\r\n<h6>Vice President, Finance and Human Resources</h6>\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="" post="" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n<h5>Mirella Lebeau</h5>\r\n<h6>VP of Client Support and Managed Services</h6>\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Testimonials</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="8/12"][vc_accordion collapsible="1"][vc_accordion_tab title="Roy French, CIO, Saint Elizabeth Health Care"][vc_column_text]"Through Kanatek’s Managed Service offerings, we have reduced the complexity of our backup/restore processes while increasing reliability. Their approach has provided solutions that are sensitive to our unique requirements, allowing us to focus our IT resources on more strategic initiatives."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Luciana Pimentel, Project Manager, Torstar Corporation"][vc_column_text]"I have been involved as a Project Manager for Torstar Corporation involving a Backup and Recovery Project. The key integrating company involved was KTI Kanatek Technologies Inc. They have proven to be an extremely strong partner with deep capabilities in data protection. From the beginning, Kanatek understood the criticality of our infrastructure stabilization project and has consistently performed on the phases of our Symantec Enterprise Backup, Archiving, Deduplication and Quantum products. With a strong project manager and a flexible delivery team, I would recommend Kanatek as a company that has an excellent professional services staff."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="George Reichert, Chief Information Officer, Nortel Networks"][vc_column_text]"Kanatek''s backup and recovery managed services team provides Nortel with the needed resources and tools to ensure the availability of our data through cost-effective solutions and unparalleled support. Data is everything and Kanatek helps us ensure the availability of our valuable resources. You can rebuild the network or rebuild a server, but you cannot rebuild your data if you lose it."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Raj Kumar, Vendor Management, CIBC Mellon Trust Company"][vc_column_text]"I would like to compliment Kanatek for their service support. CIBC Mellon holds extremely high standards for vendors and Kanatek has consistently exceeded expectations in their proactive preparation, knowledge and response time. The Kanatek team has been attentive, patient, and committed to forging a strong partnership with our organization. I am confident that we can build on this relationship and look forward to continuing to work with Kanatek."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="4/12"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Write Your Testimonial</h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][contact-form-7 id="9"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Partners</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"]<a href="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/hitachi.png"><img class=" size-full wp-image-70 aligncenter" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/hitachi.png" alt="hitachi" width="127" height="32" /></a> <a href="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/quantum.png"><img class=" size-full wp-image-73 aligncenter" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/quantum.png" alt="quantum" width="143" height="24" /></a> <a href="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/symantec.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-75" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/symantec.png" alt="symantec" width="154" height="41" /></a> <a href="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/dell.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-68" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/dell.png" alt="dell" width="51" height="51" /></a> <a href="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/oracle.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-72" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/oracle.png" alt="oracle" width="146" height="18" /></a> <a href="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/redhat.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-74" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/redhat.png" alt="redhat" width="138" height="44" /></a> <a href="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/globanet.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-69" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/globanet.png" alt="globanet" width="170" height="29" /></a> <a href="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/netapp.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-71" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/netapp.png" alt="netapp" width="46" height="52" /></a> <a href="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/clearwell.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-67" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/clearwell.png" alt="clearwell" width="159" height="40" /></a> <a href="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/terix.png"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-76" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/terix.png" alt="terix" width="99" height="39" /></a>[/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-25 04:10:55', '2015-01-25 04:10:55', '', 4, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/01/25/4-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
