(117, 1, '2015-01-25 13:36:55', '2015-01-25 13:36:55', '<img class="img-responsive alignnone wp-image-670 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/managed-services-banner.jpg" alt="managed-services-banner" width="940" height="400" />\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Kanatek’s Managed Services</h3>\r\nKanatek’s market leading Managed Services offering ensures the full operation of an organization’s global Backup &amp; Recovery environment and includes:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Monitoring and remediating backup integrity globally, 24x7[/list_item][list_item]Data recovery services in the event of a natural or man-made data loss[/list_item][list_item]Performing monthly restore audits and retention tests[/list_item][list_item]Participating in disaster recovery testing[/list_item][list_item]Managing Service Level Agreements (SLAs) and reporting on performance[/list_item][list_item]Identifying and implementing efficiencies and cost-saving processes[/list_item][list_item]Identifying opportunities to deploy new technology to further reduce costs[/list_item][list_item]Customizing reporting to each client’s needs[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\nKanatek Managed Services give clients the assurance that data is protected and accessible while allowing critical IT resources to focus on what makes the business unique.\r\n\r\n[button class="mybtn btn-orange" url="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/KTI-Managed-Services-2012.pdf" target="_blank"]Download Brochure[/button]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Managed Services', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'managed-services', '', '', '2015-05-02 14:13:46', '2015-05-02 14:13:46', '', 0, 'http://localhost/kanatek/?page_id=117', 0, 'page', '', 0),
