(165, 1, '2015-01-25 14:34:30', '2015-01-25 14:34:30', '[vc_row][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_column_text css_animation=""]\r\n<h3>Technical Architect – Ottawa, Montreal, GTA</h3>\r\nFor over 30 years, Kanatek has been designing, implementing and supporting complex solutions for its clients to help them deliver the best returns on their IT investment. Kanatek is an independent systems integrator specializing in data availability, networked storage, and back up and recovery solutions. Our headquarters are located in Ottawa with a branch office in Toronto.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5>Main responsibilities</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Provide consulting, design, and/or implementation support for data storage and protection</li>\r\n	<li>Provide technical services including installation and support for customers in a highly complex data storage environment</li>\r\n	<li>Work closely with sales, technical services and support groups, external vendor partners, and the customer to ensure a smooth implementation and transition</li>\r\n	<li>Provide general sales support for products and services, such as demonstrations, proposal preparation and bid responses</li>\r\n	<li>Develop installation documentation and operation procedures</li>\r\n	<li>Implement solutions in accordance with Kanatek standards and as per Statement of Work</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5>Requirements</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Five yrs hands-on experience (installation and support) in one or more of the following disciplines; backup and recovery software, tape technology, RAID storage products, SAN fibre architecture, Email Archiving</li>\r\n	<li>Must have excellent skills in Unix (Solaris, HP-UX, AIX) and/or Windows</li>\r\n	<li>Experience with Symantec/Veritas NetBackup and Backup Exec</li>\r\n	<li>Experience with Symantec Enterprise Vault</li>\r\n	<li>Experience with CommVault</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent knowledge of networking technologies</li>\r\n	<li>Experience working with storage products on a variety of open systems</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent analytical abilities, resulting in problem resolution</li>\r\n	<li>Excellent verbal and written communication skills</li>\r\n	<li>Ability to work independently</li>\r\n	<li>BS in Computer Science or equivalent experience</li>\r\n	<li>Experience or skills with the following a plus</li>\r\n	<li>High performance storage subsystems and SAN technologies; IP SAN; iSCSI, NAS</li>\r\n	<li>Database backup and restore such as Oracle, SQL, Exchange, SAP</li>\r\n	<li>Fibre channel fabric such as Qlogic,Brocade,McDATA switches</li>\r\n	<li>Clustered systems or high availability solutions</li>\r\n	<li>Certifications (Symantec/Veritas, EMC, Sun, HP, MCSE)</li>\r\n	<li>Email Archiving</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5>Other</h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Availability to work evenings or weekends as required</li>\r\n	<li>Occasional travel may be required</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text css_animation=""]\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in the position, please email us at <a href="mailto:hr@kanatek.com">hr@kanatek.com</a> or fill out the form below.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][contact-form-7 id="172" title="Job Application"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Technical Architect - Ottawa', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'technical-architect', '', '', '2015-04-28 00:37:12', '2015-04-28 00:37:12', '', 615, 'http://localhost/kanatek/?page_id=165', 0, 'page', '', 0),
