(291, 1, '2015-02-15 21:05:30', '2015-02-15 21:05:30', '<img class="img-responsive alignnone wp-image-678 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/nuage-solutions-banner.jpg" alt="nuage-solutions-banner" width="940" height="400" />\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Kanatek Nuage</h3>\r\nCanada’s cloud storage and integrated data management solution built exclusively for Canadian businesses continuing a 33-year history of unprecedented success in corporate data protection.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"]\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive alignnone wp-image-668 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/cloud-solutions-banner.jpg" alt="cloud-solutions-banner" width="265" height="350" />\r\n\r\n[/vc_column][vc_column width="3/4"]\r\n\r\nKanatek Nuage delivers:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]<strong>Reduced infrastructure costs</strong> - Lower expenditures on infrastructure acquisition costs, infrastructure maintenance, tape management, facilities administration and hardware maintenance.[/list_item][list_item]<strong>The elimination of tape and offsite tape storage</strong> - vastly improving your disaster recovery plan and reducing OPEX costs.[/list_item][list_item]<strong>A financial model suited to your business needs (CAPEX to OPEX) model</strong> - improving cash flow to support more strategic deployment of your capital expenditures.[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Download the Kanatek Nuage Solution Overview:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">[button class="mybtn btn-orange" url="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Kanatek-Nuage-Cloud-solution-overview-print-web.pdf" target="_blank"]Download[/button]</p>\r\n[/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Download the Kanatek Nuage Customer Case Study:</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">[button class="mybtn btn-orange" url="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Kanatek-Nuage-web-Pika-Case-Study_20150420.pdf" target="_blank"]Download[/button]</p>\r\n[/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text css_animation=""]\r\n<h3>Kanatek Nuage 100% Canadian Owned &amp; Operated</h3>\r\nEliminate the risk &amp; cost associated with complex foreign compliancy requirements with an all-Canadian solution from Kanatek.\r\n\r\nHow does an All-Canadian Cloud Solution from Kanatek protect you?\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Abides by all Canadian privacy and security regulations including PIPEDA.[/list_item][list_item]Protected from US Patriot Act which permits US government and US law enforcement agencies the right to search data retained by US hosting companies.[/list_item][list_item]Avoids burden and complexity of US taxes levied on Canadian companies hosting services in the US.[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive alignnone wp-image-688 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/canadian-flag-banner.jpg" alt="canadian-flag-banner" width="940" height="310" />', 'Cloud Solutions', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'cloud-solutions', '', '', '2015-05-02 14:08:51', '2015-05-02 14:08:51', '', 0, 'http://localhost/kanatek/?page_id=291', 0, 'page', '', 0),
