(312, 1, '2015-04-19 14:20:35', '2015-04-19 14:20:35', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>Kanatek Client Support</h3>\nMission-critical infrastructures need to be supported to protect organizations. Network failure, loss of data, or delayed access to data can all have a material effect on enterprises. Organizations protect their investments with tailored, 24x7 support contracts.\n\nKanatek Client Support is a 24x7 Data Management technical support service and provides unique value to clients. Here is what we do:\n\n[spacer height="25px"]\n<h3>Prevent escalation</h3>\n[list_arrow][list_item]Immediate access to help desk[/list_item][list_item]Bilingual 24x7x365 support[/list_item][list_item]High resolution of issues without escalation (call closure rate ~95%)[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\n<h3>Deliver a Streamlined Support Experience</h3>\n[list_arrow][list_item]High depth of knowledge in your environment[/list_item][list_item]Bilingual 24x7x365 support[/list_item][list_item]High resolution of issues without escalation (call closure rate ~95%)[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\n<h3>Prevent escalation</h3>\n[list_arrow][list_item]Immediate access to help desk[/list_item][list_item]Bilingual 24x7x365 support[/list_item][list_item]High resolution of issues without escalation (call closure rate ~95%)[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Support Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '119-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-04-19 14:20:35', '2015-04-19 14:20:35', '', 119, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/02/15/119-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
