(328, 1, '2015-02-21 12:44:13', '2015-02-21 12:44:13', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]Kanatek’s agentless multi-tenant software architecture provides for simple deployment and hands-free management while providing advanced features that include global de-duplication, automated mass deployment, autonomic healing, and validation restore capabilities. NuAge lowers the total cost of ownership, reduces recovery time objectives, and eliminates silos of backup data by providing a single consolidated repository while providing 100% recovery assurance.\r\n\r\nKanatek NuAge maintains the most complete set of capabilities in the industry with enterprises highlighting the following:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Support for physical, virtual and cloud environments[/list_item][list_item]Non-intrusive and easy to manage agentless architecture[/list_item][list_item]High-performance local and remote backup and recovery[/list_item][list_item]Long-term data recoverability to meet compliance mandates[/list_item][list_item]NIST FIPS 140-2 certified security with AES-256 encryption in-flight and at-rest for compliance readiness[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"]\r\n\r\n[feature_big_icon icon_url="../wp-content/themes/grepfrut/img/icons/icon1-cloud.png" heading="NuAge Cloud Backup v12"]<a title="Cloud Backup" href="http://localhost/kanatek/cloud-solutions/cloud-backup/">Read More</a>[/feature_big_icon]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column]\r\n\r\n[vc_column width="1/2"]\r\n\r\n[feature_big_icon icon_url="../wp-content/themes/grepfrut/img/icons/icon1-cloud.png" heading="NuAge License Model"]<a title="License Model" href="http://localhost/kanatek/cloud-solutions/license-model/">Read More</a>[/feature_big_icon]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column]\r\n\r\n[/vc_row]', 'Cloud Solutions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '123-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-21 12:44:13', '2015-02-21 12:44:13', '', 123, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/02/21/123-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(329, 1, '2015-02-21 12:44:57', '2015-02-21 12:44:57', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text css_animation=""]\r\n\r\nKanatek NuAge provides businesses that uses PaaS / SaaS based infrastructures such as Salesforce.com, Microsoft Dynamics, Google Apps or in Microsoft Azure, IBM Smartcloud, or Amazon S3 the ability to backup and restore large amounts of data in a really short time.\r\n\r\nWith a single interface for managing all backup data and complete storage hardware independent, the NuAge Cloud Backup V12:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Reduces your backup and recovery time[/list_item][list_item]Delivers high availability of data/applications[/list_item][list_item]Protect your IP[/list_item][list_item]Ensures regulatory compliance[/list_item][list_item]Ensure availability / recoverability of all your IP[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nDownload the NuAge Cloud Backup V12 product sheet:\r\n\r\n[button class="mybtn btn-orange" url="document.pdf" target="_blank"]Download[/button]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Cloud Backup', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '291-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-21 12:44:57', '2015-02-21 12:44:57', '', 291, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/02/21/291-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(330, 1, '2015-02-21 12:46:01', '2015-02-21 12:46:01', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text css_animation=""]\r\n\r\nData growth is outpacing the decline in backup prices. As a result, backup and recovery software is becoming increasingly expensive. We recognize that the market today is at another key inflection point. It’s time for a fair pricing model – one that reflects true business value and is based on performance.\r\n\r\nIntroducing the NuAge Recovery License Model (RLM) – a performance-based model that accounts for the total amount of recovery performed by you, our customer, on an annual basis. The NuAge Recovery License Model includes three core features such as; NuAge Recovery Tracker, The Recovery performance score and recovery drills.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nTo find out how the NuAge™ RLM can benefit you, download our Recovery License Model frequently asked questions:\r\n\r\n[button class="mybtn btn-orange" url="document.pdf" target="_blank"]Download[/button]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"]\r\n\r\n[vc_column_text css_animation=""]\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="question4" icon_color="#fff"]Common FAQ''s[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[vc_toggle title="How hard was it to style this page?" open="false"]Oh boy, it took me hours! Just kidding :)[/vc_toggle][vc_toggle title="What is the License Model?" open="false"]I have no clue, but Chuck Norris has the answer.[/vc_toggle][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'License Model', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '293-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-21 12:46:01', '2015-02-21 12:46:01', '', 293, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/02/21/293-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
