(364, 1, '2015-02-21 15:17:55', '2015-02-21 15:17:55', '[box style="dark"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1>[text_color]Three great reasons[/text_color] to choose the\r\n[text_color]<strong>Kanatek Decommissioning Service[/text_color]</strong> to solve your obsolete infrastructure problem</h1>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[list_unstyled][list_item]Protect your data and protect your reputation[/list_item][list_item]Work collaboratively with you to determine your business and IT needs and determine the right approach[/list_item][list_item]Manage the entire project from end-to-end[/list_item][/list_unstyled]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="10px"]\r\n\r\n[/box]\r\n\r\n[vc_empty_space height="60px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>Obsolete infrastructure in your data center is a problem.</strong></h3>\r\nIn the data centre, old infrastructure like servers and routers costs your organization money and space. These inefficiencies can cost you:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Higher maintenance costs[/list_item][list_item]Higher power consumption[/list_item][list_item]Valuable physical space[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\nIf you throw it away, you can open up sensitive data still remaining to theft and illegal use, data such as financial information or personal employee or customer information. Even if the data has been removed, improper wiping can leave behind valuable or sensitive information.\r\n\r\nDiscarding electronic equipment in landfills or improperly recycling them also causes environmental damage by leaking heavy metals into the ground or nearby water systems.  Poorly discarded infrastructure can usually be traced back to your organization through serial numbers, in turn leading to public relations issues and possibly heavy penalties.\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3><strong>Turn to Kanatek for Responsible and Ethical Decommissioning</strong></h3>\r\nKanatek’s Decommissioning Service helps you safely identify, remove and destroy obsolete infrastructure by offering end-to-end management and customized coordination of the destruction process that:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Identifies the right candidates for decommissioning[/list_item][list_item]Reduces the overhead costs incurred by old gear[/list_item][list_item]Is environmentally responsible[/list_item][list_item]Ensures data security without compromise[/list_item][list_item]Safeguards your organization’s reputation[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\nKanatek partners with Artex Environmental to ensure that decommissioned servers and other hardware are securely and ethically destroyed. Artex is a certified primary processor with the Ontario Electronic Stewardship (OES) and is certified under the National Environmental Recycling Standard 2010 as well as ISO 14001.\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>How It Works</h3>\r\n<span style="line-height: 1.5;">Kanatek manages the entire decommissioning process starting with a review of old network equipment and the identification of decommissioning candidates. We then document and provide you with a potential savings report. Next we take full responsibility for the destruction of all equipment and data.  Chain of Custody is maintained throughout for additional security.  We are committed to ensuring that decommissioning meets your business needs, protects your reputation and improves your data centre costs.</span>\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>How We Keep Your Data Secure</h3>\r\nWe know the security of your data is paramount.  With our Decommissioning Service, no assets are ever resold, removing the risk of data compromise or loss as a result of incomplete wiping or missed data.  Artex provides secure transport by bonded carriers for components that are picked up at your facility.  Destruction of all data-bearing components -- including hard drives, magnetic tape and other media -- is guaranteed and Certificates of Secure Destruction are provided for all equipment.\r\n\r\nAll Artex employees are security screened by the RCMP and monitored using world-class security and biometric systems. Artex’s secure facility protocols are also best-in-class, designed by a leading data centre and CSIS certified security consultant.\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3><strong>Additional Services Available from Kanatek</strong></h3>\r\nKanatek provide a range of additional services depending on your needs, including:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]shredding at your premises[/list_item][list_item]witnessed destruction[/list_item][list_item]video-taped destruction at the Artex facility[/list_item][list_item]hard drive destruction[/list_item][list_item]asset tag and serial number scan/match[/list_item][list_item]equipment de-installation[/list_item][list_item]national bonded logistics[/list_item][list_item]collection event management[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Decommissioning Service', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'decommissioning-service', '', '', '2015-04-19 14:38:37', '2015-04-19 14:38:37', '', 0, 'http://localhost/kanatek/?page_id=364', 0, 'page', '', 0),
