(389, 1, '2015-02-28 15:17:39', '2015-02-28 15:17:39', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Peter Karneef\r\n<small>Chief Executive Officer</small></h3>\r\nPeter is an industry pioneer in the computer technology and computer telephony industries. Following his graduation from Carleton University in Ottawa, Peter began his career as a real-time software and business systems software designer at HiTech Canada Ltd. (currently known as AIT).\r\n\r\nIn 1982, he founded Kanatek Technologies and in 1985 he co-founded PIKA Technologies (a leading developer of computer telephony platforms). As Kanatek''s CEO, Peter provides the operational and financial strategic guidance to help ensure continued stability and profitability.\r\n\r\nPeter has been named to the National Register''s Who''s Who in Executives and Professionals. The National Register recognizes individuals for their personal achievements.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Peter Karneef', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'peter-karneef', '', '', '2015-02-28 16:45:51', '2015-02-28 16:45:51', '', 4, 'http://localhost/kanatek/?page_id=389', 0, 'page', '', 0),
