(403, 1, '2015-02-28 15:44:33', '2015-02-28 15:44:33', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Michael De Cesare\r\n<small>Vice President, Finance and Human Resources</small></h3>\r\nIn addition to managing the traditional functions within Human Resources and Finance, Michael spearheads the corporate financial reporting, treasury and budgeting functions. Michael is responsible for credit management while also creating innovative financing alternatives for Kanatek clients.\r\n\r\nMichael has managed several major corporate projects over the past 20 years. Michael built an extensive and varied base of experience while working for a public accounting firm.\r\n\r\nMichael is a business graduate from the University of Ottawa and a Chartered Professional Accountant. In addition to being a struggling golfer, he is also an avid skier.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Michael De Cesare', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'michael-de-cesare', '', '', '2015-02-28 16:45:30', '2015-02-28 16:45:30', '', 4, 'http://localhost/kanatek/?page_id=403', 0, 'page', '', 0),
