(408, 1, '2015-02-28 15:48:54', '2015-02-28 15:48:54', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Darryl Levesque\r\n<small>Director, Technology Solutions</small></h3>\r\nDarryl is a graduate of George Brown College with over 25 years in related IT experience. Over his career Darryl has worked in a number of industry sectors including manufacturing, aerospace, finance, medical and many more. He brings a unique blend of expertise and experience to the table which helps him better understand customer needs.\r\n\r\nPrior to joining Kanatek Darryl held various positions, from senior management to field services. He was a Senior Manager – Technical Services for a worldwide logistics and warehousing company and also worked in the financial sector managing a team that supported business critical systems.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Darryl Levesque', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'darryl-levesque', '', '', '2015-02-28 16:45:16', '2015-02-28 16:45:16', '', 4, 'http://localhost/kanatek/?page_id=408', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(409, 1, '2015-02-28 15:48:54', '2015-02-28 15:48:54', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Darryl Levesque\r\n<small>Director, Technology Solutions</small></h3>\r\nDarryl is a graduate of George Brown College with over 25 years in related IT experience. Over his career Darryl has worked in a number of industry sectors including manufacturing, aerospace, finance, medical and many more. He brings a unique blend of expertise and experience to the table which helps him better understand customer needs.\r\n\r\nPrior to joining Kanatek Darryl held various positions, from senior management to field services. He was a Senior Manager – Technical Services for a worldwide logistics and warehousing company and also worked in the financial sector managing a team that supported business critical systems.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Darryl Levesque', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '408-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-28 15:48:54', '2015-02-28 15:48:54', '', 408, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/02/28/408-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(410, 1, '2015-02-28 15:50:20', '2015-02-28 15:50:20', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>David Kerrivan\r\n<small>Sr. Manager, Client Support and Managed Services</small></h3>\r\nDavid is responsible for the day to day management of all services related activities. His primary responsibilities include client support, project management and delivery. David is dedicated to ensuring exceptional client service.\r\n\r\nDavid joined Kanatek in 1996 as a customer support representative and worked in all areas of the company’s services offerings.\r\n\r\nDavid is a graduate of Algonquin College’s Computer Engineering Technology program. Among his many personal interests, is helping mentor youth through the Scouting movement.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'David Kerrivan', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'david-kerrivan', '', '', '2015-04-30 23:17:44', '2015-04-30 23:17:44', '', 4, 'http://localhost/kanatek/?page_id=410', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(411, 1, '2015-02-28 15:50:20', '2015-02-28 15:50:20', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Mirella Lebeau\r\n<small>Vice President, Client Support and Managed Services</small></h3>\r\nMirella, is responsible for the day-to -day strategic management of all services related activities. Her primary responsibilities include client support, project management, delivery and architectural services, as well as overall business planning, budgeting, and marketing strategies. Mirella is committed to driving strategic results and ensuring superior and satisfied client experiences.\r\n\r\nMirella joined the Company in 2006 after being a tactical client for Kanatek during her tenure as a Manager at Nortel as well as Computer Science Corporation (CSC). She led several professional services teams at both of these organizations.\r\n\r\nMirella is a graduate of Psychology from Carleton University, and also holds an Ontario Management Development Program Leadership certification.\r\n\r\nMirella’s personal interests include; hiking, traveling and gourmet cooking.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Mirella Lebeau', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '410-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-28 15:50:20', '2015-02-28 15:50:20', '', 410, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/02/28/410-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(412, 1, '2015-02-28 15:51:11', '2015-02-28 15:51:11', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Peter Karneef\r\n<small>Chief Executive Officer</small></h3>\r\nPeter is an industry pioneer in the computer technology and computer telephony industries. Following his graduation from Carleton University in Ottawa, Peter began his career as a real-time software and business systems software designer at HiTech Canada Ltd. (currently known as AIT).\r\n\r\nIn 1982, he founded Kanatek Technologies and in 1985 he co-founded PIKA Technologies (a leading developer of computer telephony platforms). As Kanatek''s CEO, Peter provides the operational and financial strategic guidance to help ensure continued stability and profitability.\r\n\r\nPeter has been named to the National Register''s Who''s Who in Executives and Professionals. The National Register recognizes individuals for their personal achievements.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Peter Karneef', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '389-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-28 15:51:11', '2015-02-28 15:51:11', '', 389, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/02/28/389-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(413, 1, '2015-02-28 15:51:41', '2015-02-28 15:51:41', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Andrew Maknyik\r\n<small>National Director of Sales</small></h3>\r\nAndrew is a graduate of York University (Economics), and also holds a Diploma in Marketing. As our National Director of Sales, Andrew oversees the overall coordination, functional management, and leadership of our sales initiatives. Over his career, Andrew has worked in various sales capacities within the IT sector, with an extensive background in hardware, software and services. He has supported a diverse background of clientele, including Manufacturing, Health Care, Utilities, Insurance, and Telco. His history working within these sectors, as well as working with several different vendors, has led him to develop a strong insight into market trends, and differing technologies. Andrew has a passion for delivering value to our clients, and is always looking for a way to help them improve the performance of their business through technology.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Andrew Maknyik', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '405-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-28 15:51:41', '2015-02-28 15:51:41', '', 405, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/02/28/405-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(414, 1, '2015-02-28 15:52:30', '2015-02-28 15:52:30', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Michael De Cesare\r\n<small>Vice President, Finance and Human Resources</small></h3>\r\nIn addition to managing the traditional functions within Human Resources and Finance, Michael spearheads the corporate financial reporting, treasury and budgeting functions. Michael is responsible for credit management while also creating innovative financing alternatives for Kanatek clients.\r\n\r\nMichael has managed several major corporate projects over the past 20 years. Michael built an extensive and varied base of experience while working for a public accounting firm.\r\n\r\nMichael is a business graduate from the University of Ottawa and a Chartered Professional Accountant. In addition to being a struggling golfer, he is also an avid skier.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Michael De Cesare', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '403-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-28 15:52:30', '2015-02-28 15:52:30', '', 403, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/02/28/403-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
