(437, 1, '2015-04-03 13:29:39', '2015-04-03 13:29:39', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>Kanatek Email Archiving Services</strong></h3>\r\nKanatek’s Email Archiving Services deliver an effective search and retrieval process for email systems.\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3><strong>Invest In The Best Email Search &amp; Retrieval System</strong></h3>\r\nEnterprise Vault™ software from VERITAS combines the capability of an efficient archive mechanism with the power of a search engine to provide instant, flexible access to the message store. It offers a centralized archiving framework for information held in: Microsoft Exchange, File Systems, Microsoft SharePoint™ Portal Server, IBM Domino™, Journal Email and SMTP.\r\n\r\nBenefits:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Up to 60% reduction in electronic storage costs[/list_item][list_item]Compliance for archiving of electronic correspondence[/list_item][list_item]Deliver flexible content storage[/list_item][list_item]Reduce storage via compression and single-instancing[/list_item][list_item]Removal of the PST headache for administrators and users[/list_item][list_item]Index content for rapid and targeted retrieval[/list_item][list_item]Secure future accessibility regardless of application[/list_item][list_item]Employ user authentication security controls[/list_item][list_item]Define and implement retention and expiration policies[/list_item][list_item]Ensure access to archived data from any device[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3><strong>Build an Intelligent Information Management System</strong></h3>\r\nAn intelligent Information Management System complies with retention and deletion policies that keep information only for as long as needed. Backup &amp; Recovery times of archived platforms are greatly reduced by moving older, infrequently accessed data. Overall Backup &amp; Recovery times are further streamlined by the benefits of single instance storage into a centralized archive.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Email Archiving', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'email-archiving', '', '', '2015-04-03 13:30:40', '2015-04-03 13:30:40', '', 0, 'http://localhost/kanatek/?page_id=437', 0, 'page', '', 0),
