(465, 1, '2015-04-19 14:29:04', '2015-04-19 14:29:04', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Kanatek Client Support (KCS)</h3>\r\nMission-critical infrastructures need to be supported to protect organizations. Network failure, loss of data, or delayed access to data can all have a material effect on enterprises. Organizations protect their investments with tailored, 24x7 support contracts.\r\n\r\nKanatek Client Support is a 24x7 Data Management technical support service and provides unique value to clients. Here is what we do:\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Prevent escalation</h3>\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Immediate access to help desk[/list_item][list_item]Bilingual 24x7x365 support[/list_item][list_item]High resolution of issues without escalation (call closure rate ~95%)[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Deliver a Streamlined Support Experience</h3>\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]High depth of knowledge in your environment[/list_item][list_item]Ability to consolidate contract management[/list_item][list_item]Customized SLAs that can result in faster response times[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Multi-Vendor Support</h3>\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Kanatek has deep understanding of your heterogeneous IT environment[/list_item][list_item]Kanatek will resolve problems involving multiple vendors to deliver seamless and appropriate solutions and support[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Support', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '119-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-19 14:29:04', '2015-04-19 14:29:04', '', 119, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/04/19/119-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(466, 1, '2015-04-19 14:32:11', '2015-04-19 14:32:11', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="embed-container"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/4wwuZJbNnI4?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0" width="300" height="150" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></div>\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Kanatek Assessments</h3>\r\nThe Kanatek Enterprise Assessment is a Professional Service engagement that identifies potential issues that can impact your IT operations and delivers qualified recommendations to improve service levels. A Kanatek Enterprise Assessment can have many benefits to your organization. Here are just a few:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Identify areas of poor performance and infrastructure bottlenecks.[/list_item][list_item]Perform a gap analysis and document the results for management.[/list_item][list_item]Identify license oversubscriptions or gaps.[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Our Approach</h3>\r\nOur team of data management specialists provides an analysis of your backup and recovery, data archiving or storage environment.\r\n\r\nOur thorough data collection process is followed by an in-depth analysis stage. This allows us to identify and report on deficiencies in your storage and data management infrastructure and provide recommendations that will rectify issues in tactical and strategic focus areas.\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]<strong>Assessment Scope Definition</strong> - Our specialists will meet with your team to define your specific goals and objectives from the assessment. The scope could include all or one of the following; the evaluation of policy, process, operations and server and storage infrastructure.[/list_item][list_item]<strong>Data Collection and Analysis</strong> - Our specialists will collaborate with your team to collect and analyze required data as agreed to in the requirements definition phase, using infrastructure data collection and staff interviews.[/list_item][list_item]<strong>Findings and Recommendations</strong> - We then present to you our findings in a detailed report, along with any technical and operational recommendations for improvement.[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Why Choose Kanatek?</h3>\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Kanatek‘s infrastructure optimization practice includes resources with many years of IT experience.[/list_item][list_item]Technology agnostic – Kanatek can freely recommend best practices approach[/list_item][list_item]The Kanatek values: Trusted, Ethical, Flexible, Creative, Focused, Enduring.[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Assessment', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'assessment', '', '', '2015-04-28 00:53:46', '2015-04-28 00:53:46', '', 0, 'http://localhost/kanatek/?page_id=466', 0, 'page', '', 0),
