(490, 1, '2015-04-19 15:18:58', '2015-04-19 15:18:58', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\nKeeping pace with the speed and complexity of change in data management is time-consuming and distracts an organization from its core priorities. It is also a costly exercise: managing infrastructure, maintaining resources, understanding data complexities, and complying with legislation.\r\n\r\nThat’s why we have been consulting successfully for 30 years. We believe that data management should be an investment, not a cost. IT should help a company gain a competitive advantage. IT should enable data insight and mobilize the effective leverage of an organization’s data - as one of its key assets.\r\n\r\n[blockquote]We can help you gain this advantage from IT.[/blockquote]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Managing the Growth In Data</h3>\r\nIT is evolving from a system-centric model to an information-centric model. With fewer resources and lower budgets being allocated to IT departments, companies are in a tight squeeze.\r\n\r\nBut that is where external data management consulting and services can help. Our clients access knowledgeable, specialized expertise that can quickly assess their situation and design a pragmatic solution best suited to their environment.\r\n\r\n[blockquote]We understand the pressure in corporate IT departments.[/blockquote]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Bringing an Independent Perspective</h3>\r\nTo ensure that we are developing customized data management solutions for our clients’ unique needs and environments, we partner with the best technology innovators.\r\n\r\nNo two clients are alike; no two solutions are alike. Our system architects and engineers are among the most experienced in the industry. They bring critical thinking and an independent, unbiased perspective to clients challenged with managing risk and compliance.\r\n\r\n[blockquote]We bring informed experience to Data Management challenges.[/blockquote]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>A Trusted IT Partner</h3>\r\nWe have earned a reputation as a trusted data management partner from some of the world’s most successful enterprises.\r\n\r\nOur clients trust us to recommend, architect, install and support solutions that are designed for their mission-critical, enterprise-level environments. They value our knowledge base of best practices, our years of specialism and our ability to deliver on time and on budget.\r\n\r\n[blockquote]We are trusted by our clients.[/blockquote]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>A Consultative Approach</h3>\r\nOrganizations appreciate the depth and maturity of our experienced team. Whether it’s presenting to executives or working with technical experts, we focus on solutions that improve the total cost of ownership and maximize return on investment.\r\n\r\nOur technical team is relentlessly expanding its knowledge base and upgrading its certifications as new technology is introduced. We want to ensure our advice is well-informed and complete.\r\n\r\n[blockquote]We invest in our team.[/blockquote]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>A Client-centric Process</h3>\r\nWe utilize a four-part, end-to-end engagement model that delivers custom data management solutions to meet the business needs of our clients:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]<a title="Assess" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/aims-methodology/assess/"><strong>Assess &amp; Architect</strong></a> - identify technical and operational areas for new efficiencies, deliver optimization insight and design new architectures[/list_item][list_item]<a title="Integrate" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/aims-methodology/integrate/"><strong>Integrate &amp; Implement</strong></a> - deploy new solutions and system upgrades, oversee projects and resources and perform data migration[/list_item][list_item]<a title="Manage" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/aims-methodology/manage/"><strong>Manage &amp; Optimize</strong></a> - direct Backup &amp; Recovery operations, provide remote Data Management and availability services and offer dedicated on-site IT resources[/list_item][list_item]<a title="Support" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/aims-methodology/support/"><strong>Support &amp; Maintain</strong></a> - retain around-the-clock technical help desk and support, service both software and hardware solutions and manage multi-vendor interactions[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\n[blockquote]We focus on how best to serve our clients needs.[/blockquote]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Corporate Profile', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'corporate-profile', '', '', '2015-04-19 15:46:26', '2015-04-19 15:46:26', '', 4, 'http://localhost/kanatek/?page_id=490', 0, 'page', '', 0),
