(497, 1, '2015-04-19 15:26:05', '2015-04-19 15:26:05', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Enhance the efficiency of your backup and recovery software, hardware assets, and IT resources</h3>\r\nKanatek''s Professional Services team can implement reliable solutions that offer:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Guaranteed data backups[/list_item][list_item]Data recoverability[/list_item][list_item]Reduced impact on your business[/list_item][list_item]Minimal system downtime[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\nKanatek answers the need for enterprise backup control and rationalization with solutions that deliver a single, centralized point of control for managing backup, from the desktop to the server.\r\n\r\nWith over 30 years of technical experience with Symantec and Oracle products, the Kanatek team provides first class implementations and customized upgrades - tailoring and optimizing solutions to fit your organization''s needs.\r\n\r\nContact us at <a href="mailto:info@kanatek.com">info@kanatek.com</a> for more information on how Kanatek can help deploy your backup solutions.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Integrate', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'integrate', '', '', '2015-05-02 14:19:58', '2015-05-02 14:19:58', '', 492, 'http://localhost/kanatek/?page_id=497', 0, 'page', '', 0),
