ific need or want look at your overall infrastructure and processes to promote efficiencies, we can help.\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"]\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive alignnone wp-image-516 size-medium" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/AIMS-I-300x266.png" alt="AIMS-I" width="300" height="266" />\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><a title="Integrate" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/aims-methodology/integrate/"><strong>Integrate &amp; Implement</strong></a></h3>\r\nServices can help you realize the benefits of a tightly aligned IT infrastructure.\r\n\r\nWe will work closely with you to achieve your strategy of integrating complex, backup &amp; recovery software, hardware assets, and related IT resources to create an enterprise wide information flow solution that is designed to be flexible and cost-effective.\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"]\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive alignnone wp-image-514 size-medium" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/AIMS-M-300x259.png" alt="AIMS-M" width="300" height="259" />\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><a title="Manage" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/aims-methodology/manage/"><strong>Manage &amp; Optimize</strong></a></h3>\r\nBy proactively monitoring your backup environment we are ensuring your data is secure and recoverable. Our remote niche service allows for peace of mind knowing your data is being protected. Allowing our team to manage your backup &amp; recovery infrastructure allows for ROIs by the reduction and/or elimination of hardware as well as software licenses from production sites, all the while ensuring data integrity.\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"]\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive alignnone wp-image-515 size-medium" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/AIMS-S-300x289.png" alt="AIMS-S" width="300" height="289" />\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><a title="Support" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/aims-methodology/support/"><strong>Support &amp; Maintain</strong></a></h3>\r\nKanatek technical support staff consists of highly skilled certified bilingual resources who provide quick responses to support issues 24 hours a day. Our stringent SLA’s allow for over 98% resolution internally without escalation to our partner vendors.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'AIMS Methodology', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '492-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-19 16:11:23', '2015-04-19 16:11:23', '', 492, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/04/19/492-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
