(577, 1, '2015-04-22 01:37:32', '2015-04-22 01:37:32', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Kanatek’s market leading Managed Services offering ensures the full operation of an organization’s global Backup &amp; Recovery environment and includes:</h3>\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Monitoring and remediating backup integrity globally, 24x7[/list_item][list_item]Data recovery services in the event of a natural or man-made data loss[/list_item][list_item]Performing monthly restore audits and retention tests[/list_item][list_item]Participating in disaster recovery testing[/list_item][list_item]Managing Service Level Agreements (SLAs) and reporting on performance[/list_item][list_item]Identifying and implementing efficiencies and cost-saving processes[/list_item][list_item]Identifying opportunities to deploy new technology to further reduce costs[/list_item][list_item]Customizing reporting to each client’s needs[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\nKanatek Managed Services give clients the assurance that data is protected and accessible while allowing critical IT resources to focus on what makes the business unique.\r\n\r\n[button class="mybtn btn-orange" url="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/KTI-Managed-Services-2012.pdf" target="_blank"]Download Brochure[/button]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Managed Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '117-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-22 01:37:32', '2015-04-22 01:37:32', '', 117, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/04/22/117-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(578, 1, '2015-04-22 01:38:30', '2015-04-22 01:38:30', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Obsolete infrastructure in your data centre is a problem</h3>\r\nIn the data centre, old infrastructure like servers and routers costs your organization money and space. These inefficiencies can cost you:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Higher maintenance costs.[/list_item][list_item]Higher power consumption.[/list_item][list_item]Valuable physical space.[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\nIf you throw it away, you can open up sensitive data still remaining to theft and illegal use, data such as financial information or personal employee or customer information. Even if the data has been removed, improper wiping can leave behind valuable or sensitive information.\r\n\r\nDiscarding electronic equipment in landfills or improperly recycling them also causes environmental damage by leaking heavy metals into the ground or nearby water systems. Poorly discarded infrastructure can usually be traced back to your organization through serial numbers, in turn leading to public relations issues and possibly heavy penalties.\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Turn to Kanatek for Responsible and Ethical Decommissioning</h3>\r\nKanatek’s Decommissioning Service helps you safely identify, remove and destroy obsolete infrastructure by offering end-to-end management and customized coordination of the destruction process that:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Identifies the right candidates for decommissioning[/list_item][list_item]Reduces the overhead costs incurred by old gear[/list_item][list_item]Is environmentally responsible[/list_item][list_item]Ensures data security without compromise[/list_item][list_item]Safeguards your organization’s reputation[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\nKanatek partners with Artex Environmental to ensure that decommissioned servers and other hardware are securely and ethically destroyed. Artex is a certified primary processor with the Ontario Electronic Stewardship (OES) and is certified under the National Environmental Recycling Standard 2010 as well as ISO 14001.\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Three great reasons to choose the Kanatek Decommissioning Service to solve your obsolete infrastructure problem:</h3>\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Protect your data and protect your reputation.[/list_item][list_item]Work collaboratively with you to determine your business and IT needs and determine the right approach.[/list_item][list_item]Manage the entire project from end-to-end.[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\n[button class="mybtn btn-orange" url="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Kanatek-Nuage-Cloud-solution-overview-print-web.pdf" target="_blank"]Download Brochure[/button]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Decommissioning', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '472-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-22 01:38:30', '2015-04-22 01:38:30', '', 472, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/04/22/472-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
