(599, 1, '2015-04-27 21:56:46', '2015-04-27 21:56:46', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text css_animation=""]\r\n\r\nKanatek Nuage provides businesses that uses PaaS / SaaS based infrastructures such as Salesforce.com, Microsoft Dynamics, Google Apps or in Microsoft Azure, IBM Smartcloud, or Amazon S3 the ability to backup and restore large amounts of data in a really short time.\r\n\r\nWith a single interface for managing all backup data and complete storage hardware independent, the Nuage Cloud Backup V12:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Reduces your backup and recovery time[/list_item][list_item]Delivers high availability of data/applications[/list_item][list_item]Protect your IP[/list_item][list_item]Ensures regulatory compliance[/list_item][list_item]Ensure availability / recoverability of all your IP[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nDownload the Nuage Cloud Backup V12 product sheet:\r\n\r\n[button class="mybtn btn-orange" url="document.pdf" target="_blank"]Download[/button]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Cloud Solutions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '291-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-27 21:56:46', '2015-04-27 21:56:46', '', 291, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/04/27/291-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
