(613, 1, '2015-04-28 00:20:08', '2015-04-28 00:20:08', '<a href="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/about-us-bg.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-612" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/about-us-bg.jpg" alt="about-us-bg" width="2000" height="600" /></a>\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Why we [text_color color]standout[/text_color] in a crowd</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\nKanatek provides specialized on-premise and cloud-based services for safeguarding, managing, and supporting data infrastructure.\r\n\r\nHeadquartered in Ottawa, Kanatek also has offices and a team of IT professionals in both Toronto and Montreal.\r\n\r\nSince 1982, with its extensive background and deep expertise, Kanatek has worked with IT departments across Canada, the United States, and Europe - delivering, supporting, and managing complex enterprise calibre storage, data management and server solutions.\r\n\r\nIn addition, Kanatek also offers Canada’s premier cloud storage and integrated data management solutions exclusively for Canadian businesses – continuing a 33-year history of unprecedented success in corporate data protection.\r\n\r\nKanatek solutions answer the most demanding, mission-critical challenges facing global enterprises today and our customers trust us to deliver value and expertise to protect their precious data wherever it may reside.\r\n\r\nAs an integrator and professional services provider, Kanatek adds value to our clients'' IT environments by helping them understand and integrate new technologies through leveraging their existing investments and infrastructure.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Our Mission</h3>\r\nKanatek''s mission is to provide our clients with specialized services for safeguarding, managing, and supporting their data infrastructure.  We understand how important your data is to your business and we are here to provide our subject matter expertise.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Our Values</h3>\r\nWe have been fortunate enough to hold a longevity that is rare in this business and it is our belief that our corporate values and people can be attributed to this success.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Our Corporate Values</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="infinity2" icon_color="#fff"]Enduring[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe have built a reputation of dependable performance since 1982.\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="megaphone5" icon_color="#fff"]Flexible[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe listen and respond quickly to our clients'' needs.\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="focus" icon_color="#fff"]Focused[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe are focused on delivering value in everything we do.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="spell-check" icon_color="#fff"]Ethical[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe fulfill our promises with care, honesty, and respect.\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="tools" icon_color="#fff"]Creative[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe use imagination and originality to serve our clients.\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="heart6" icon_color="#fff"]Trusted[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe forge lasting relationships with our clients and partners.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">The Team</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=""]\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="group2" icon_color="#fff"]Principles[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="Peter Karneef" post="Chief Executive Officer" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="http://settingsca.linkedin.com/pub/pierre-peter-karneef/" mail="" link=""]\r\n\r\nPeter is Kanatek’s CEO and provides the operational, financial and strategic guidance to help ensure the company’s continued stability and profitability. <a title="Peter Karneef" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/peter-karneef/">Read more...</a>\r\n\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="Terry Kell" post="President" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n\r\nTerry is the President of Kanatek, where he has worked since 1985. Terry has built the company into a respected Enterprise Storage Solutions provider. His primary focus is sales and marketing. <a title="Terry Kell" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/terry-kell/">Read more...</a>\r\n\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text css_animation=""]\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="group2" icon_color="#fff"]Management[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="Andrew Maknyik" post="National Director of Sales" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="http://ca.linkedin.com/in/amaknyik/en" mail="" link=""]\r\n\r\nAs our National Director of Sales, Andrew oversees the overall coordination, functional management, and leadership of our sales initiatives. <a title="Andrew Maknyik" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/andrew-maknyik/">Read more...</a>\r\n\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="Darryl Levesque" post="Director, Technology Solutions" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n\r\nAs the Director of Technology Solutions, Darryl brings a unique blend of expertise and experience to the table that helps him better understand customer needs. <a title="Darryl Levesque" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/darryl-levesque/">Read more...</a>\r\n\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="Michael De Cesare" post="Vice President, Finance and Human Resources" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n\r\nIn addition to managing the traditional functions within Human Resources and Finance, Michael spearheads the corporate financial reporting, treasury and budgeting functions. <a title="Michael De Cesare" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/michael-de-cesare/">Read more...</a>\r\n\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="Mirella Lebeau" post="Vice President, Client Support and Managed Services" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n\r\nMirella, is responsible for the day-to-day strategic management of all services. Her responsibilities include client support, project management, delivery and architectural services, as well as overall business planning. <a title="Mirella Lebeau" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/mirella-lebeau/">Read more...</a>\r\n\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Testimonials</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="8/12"][vc_accordion collapsible="1"][vc_accordion_tab title="Roy French, CIO, Saint Elizabeth Health Care"][vc_column_text]"Through Kanatek’s Managed Service offerings, we have reduced the complexity of our backup/restore processes while increasing reliability. Their approach has provided solutions that are sensitive to our unique requirements, allowing us to focus our IT resources on more strategic initiatives."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Luciana Pimentel, Project Manager, Torstar Corporation"][vc_column_text]"Kanatek have proven to be an extremely strong partner with deep capabilities in data protection. From the beginning, Kanatek understood the criticality of our infrastructure stabilization project. With a strong project manager and a flexible delivery team, I would recommend Kanatek as a company that has an excellent professional services staff."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="George Reichert, Chief Information Officer, Nortel Networks"][vc_column_text]"Kanatek''s backup and recovery managed services team provides Nortel with the needed resources and tools to ensure the availability of our data through cost-effective solutions and unparalleled support. Data is everything and Kanatek helps us ensure the availability of our valuable resources. You can rebuild the network or rebuild a server, but you cannot rebuild your data if you lose it."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Raj Kumar, Vendor Management, CIBC Mellon Trust Company"][vc_column_text]"I would like to compliment Kanatek for their service support. CIBC Mellon holds extremely high standards for vendors and Kanatek has consistently exceeded expectations in their proactive preparation, knowledge and response time. The Kanatek team has been attentive, patient, and committed to forging a strong partnership with our organization. I am confident that we can build on this relationship and look forward to continuing to work with Kanatek."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Wojciech Tryc, CTO, PIKA"][vc_column_text]"The Nuage agentless solution, in our view, dramatically enhanced security as it removed vulnerable points of attack that are often associated with agent-based architectures."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Glen Cain, Senior Systems Analyst, Durham Regional Police Services"][vc_column_text]"Kanatek delivers the right people for the project. I know if I have any problems at all, it’s just a quick phone call and everything is figured out. Their familiarity with various servers and their history in supplying services to large companies was important to us. These are things that make us happy as a Kanatek customer. With Kanatek, you get personal, reliable service."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="4/12"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Write Your Testimonial</h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][contact-form-7 id="9"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Partners</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][box style="light"][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<div class="text-center">\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-70" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/hitachi.png" alt="hitachi" width="127" height="32" /><img class=" size-full wp-image-73 alignnone" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/quantum.png" alt="quantum" width="143" height="24" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-75" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/symantec.png" alt="symantec" width="154" height="41" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-68" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/dell.png" alt="dell" width="51" height="51" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-72" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/oracle.png" alt="oracle" width="146" height="18" />\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-74" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/redhat.png" alt="redhat" width="138" height="44" /><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-69" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/globanet.png" alt="globanet" width="170" height="29" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-71" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/netapp.png" alt="netapp" width="46" height="52" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-67" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/clearwell.png" alt="clearwell" width="159" height="40" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-76" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/terix.png" alt="terix" width="99" height="39" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/box][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-28 00:20:08', '2015-04-28 00:20:08', '', 4, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/04/28/4-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(614, 1, '2015-04-28 00:20:52', '2015-04-28 00:20:52', '<img class="alignnone wp-image-612 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/about-us-bg.jpg" alt="about-us-bg" width="2000" height="600" />\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Why we [text_color color]standout[/text_color] in a crowd</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\nKanatek provides specialized on-premise and cloud-based services for safeguarding, managing, and supporting data infrastructure.\r\n\r\nHeadquartered in Ottawa, Kanatek also has offices and a team of IT professionals in both Toronto and Montreal.\r\n\r\nSince 1982, with its extensive background and deep expertise, Kanatek has worked with IT departments across Canada, the United States, and Europe - delivering, supporting, and managing complex enterprise calibre storage, data management and server solutions.\r\n\r\nIn addition, Kanatek also offers Canada’s premier cloud storage and integrated data management solutions exclusively for Canadian businesses – continuing a 33-year history of unprecedented success in corporate data protection.\r\n\r\nKanatek solutions answer the most demanding, mission-critical challenges facing global enterprises today and our customers trust us to deliver value and expertise to protect their precious data wherever it may reside.\r\n\r\nAs an integrator and professional services provider, Kanatek adds value to our clients'' IT environments by helping them understand and integrate new technologies through leveraging their existing investments and infrastructure.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Our Mission</h3>\r\nKanatek''s mission is to provide our clients with specialized services for safeguarding, managing, and supporting their data infrastructure.  We understand how important your data is to your business and we are here to provide our subject matter expertise.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Our Values</h3>\r\nWe have been fortunate enough to hold a longevity that is rare in this business and it is our belief that our corporate values and people can be attributed to this success.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Our Corporate Values</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="infinity2" icon_color="#fff"]Enduring[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe have built a reputation of dependable performance since 1982.\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="megaphone5" icon_color="#fff"]Flexible[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe listen and respond quickly to our clients'' needs.\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="focus" icon_color="#fff"]Focused[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe are focused on delivering value in everything we do.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="spell-check" icon_color="#fff"]Ethical[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe fulfill our promises with care, honesty, and respect.\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="tools" icon_color="#fff"]Creative[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe use imagination and originality to serve our clients.\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="heart6" icon_color="#fff"]Trusted[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\nWe forge lasting relationships with our clients and partners.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">The Team</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css_animation=""]\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="group2" icon_color="#fff"]Principles[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="Peter Karneef" post="Chief Executive Officer" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="http://settingsca.linkedin.com/pub/pierre-peter-karneef/" mail="" link=""]\r\n\r\nPeter is Kanatek’s CEO and provides the operational, financial and strategic guidance to help ensure the company’s continued stability and profitability. <a title="Peter Karneef" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/peter-karneef/">Read more...</a>\r\n\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="Terry Kell" post="President" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n\r\nTerry is the President of Kanatek, where he has worked since 1985. Terry has built the company into a respected Enterprise Storage Solutions provider. His primary focus is sales and marketing. <a title="Terry Kell" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/terry-kell/">Read more...</a>\r\n\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text css_animation=""]\r\n\r\n[icon_font_heading icon_type="group2" icon_color="#fff"]Management[/icon_font_heading]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="Andrew Maknyik" post="National Director of Sales" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="http://ca.linkedin.com/in/amaknyik/en" mail="" link=""]\r\n\r\nAs our National Director of Sales, Andrew oversees the overall coordination, functional management, and leadership of our sales initiatives. <a title="Andrew Maknyik" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/andrew-maknyik/">Read more...</a>\r\n\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="Darryl Levesque" post="Director, Technology Solutions" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n\r\nAs the Director of Technology Solutions, Darryl brings a unique blend of expertise and experience to the table that helps him better understand customer needs. <a title="Darryl Levesque" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/darryl-levesque/">Read more...</a>\r\n\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="Michael De Cesare" post="Vice President, Finance and Human Resources" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n\r\nIn addition to managing the traditional functions within Human Resources and Finance, Michael spearheads the corporate financial reporting, treasury and budgeting functions. <a title="Michael De Cesare" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/michael-de-cesare/">Read more...</a>\r\n\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="Mirella Lebeau" post="Vice President, Client Support and Managed Services" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n\r\nMirella, is responsible for the day-to-day strategic management of all services. Her responsibilities include client support, project management, delivery and architectural services, as well as overall business planning. <a title="Mirella Lebeau" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/mirella-lebeau/">Read more...</a>\r\n\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Testimonials</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="8/12"][vc_accordion collapsible="1"][vc_accordion_tab title="Roy French, CIO, Saint Elizabeth Health Care"][vc_column_text]"Through Kanatek’s Managed Service offerings, we have reduced the complexity of our backup/restore processes while increasing reliability. Their approach has provided solutions that are sensitive to our unique requirements, allowing us to focus our IT resources on more strategic initiatives."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Luciana Pimentel, Project Manager, Torstar Corporation"][vc_column_text]"Kanatek have proven to be an extremely strong partner with deep capabilities in data protection. From the beginning, Kanatek understood the criticality of our infrastructure stabilization project. With a strong project manager and a flexible delivery team, I would recommend Kanatek as a company that has an excellent professional services staff."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="George Reichert, Chief Information Officer, Nortel Networks"][vc_column_text]"Kanatek''s backup and recovery managed services team provides Nortel with the needed resources and tools to ensure the availability of our data through cost-effective solutions and unparalleled support. Data is everything and Kanatek helps us ensure the availability of our valuable resources. You can rebuild the network or rebuild a server, but you cannot rebuild your data if you lose it."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Raj Kumar, Vendor Management, CIBC Mellon Trust Company"][vc_column_text]"I would like to compliment Kanatek for their service support. CIBC Mellon holds extremely high standards for vendors and Kanatek has consistently exceeded expectations in their proactive preparation, knowledge and response time. The Kanatek team has been attentive, patient, and committed to forging a strong partnership with our organization. I am confident that we can build on this relationship and look forward to continuing to work with Kanatek."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Wojciech Tryc, CTO, PIKA"][vc_column_text]"The Nuage agentless solution, in our view, dramatically enhanced security as it removed vulnerable points of attack that are often associated with agent-based architectures."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Glen Cain, Senior Systems Analyst, Durham Regional Police Services"][vc_column_text]"Kanatek delivers the right people for the project. I know if I have any problems at all, it’s just a quick phone call and everything is figured out. Their familiarity with various servers and their history in supplying services to large companies was important to us. These are things that make us happy as a Kanatek customer. With Kanatek, you get personal, reliable service."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][/vc_accordion][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="4/12"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Write Your Testimonial</h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][contact-form-7 id="9"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Partners</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/1"][box style="light"][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<div class="text-center">\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-70" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/hitachi.png" alt="hitachi" width="127" height="32" /><img class=" size-full wp-image-73 alignnone" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/quantum.png" alt="quantum" width="143" height="24" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-75" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/symantec.png" alt="symantec" width="154" height="41" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-68" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/dell.png" alt="dell" width="51" height="51" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-72" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/oracle.png" alt="oracle" width="146" height="18" />\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-74" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/redhat.png" alt="redhat" width="138" height="44" /><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-69" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/globanet.png" alt="globanet" width="170" height="29" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-71" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/netapp.png" alt="netapp" width="46" height="52" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-67" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/clearwell.png" alt="clearwell" width="159" height="40" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-76" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/terix.png" alt="terix" width="99" height="39" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/box][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-28 00:20:52', '2015-04-28 00:20:52', '', 4, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/04/28/4-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
