(630, 1, '2015-04-30 22:06:11', '2015-04-30 22:06:11', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"]\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive aligncenter wp-image-75 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/symantec.png" alt="symantec" width="154" height="41" />\r\n\r\n[/vc_column][vc_column width="3/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Symantec</h3>\r\nKanatek Technologies is a Symantec Gold Partner and has worked with the company for over 20 years. We are one of only seven Symantec Technical Services Partner Program (TSPP) partners qualified in the world to offer first and second level support on Symantec products and the only one in Canada.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"]\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive aligncenter wp-image-69 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/globanet.png" alt="globanet" width="170" height="29" />\r\n\r\n[/vc_column][vc_column width="3/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Globanet</h3>\r\nA leading provider of archiving and e-discovery solutions, Globanet is a pioneer in archiving and intelligent information governance.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"]\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive aligncenter wp-image-68 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/dell.png" alt="dell" width="51" height="51" />\r\n\r\n[/vc_column][vc_column width="3/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Dell</h3>\r\nDell empowers customers and people everywhere to use technology to realize their dreams. Customers trust us to deliver technology solutions that help them do and achieve more, whether they’re at home, work, school or anywhere in their world.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"]\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive aligncenter wp-image-70 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/hitachi.png" alt="hitachi" width="127" height="32" />\r\n\r\n[/vc_column][vc_column width="3/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Hitachi</h3>\r\nHitachi Data Systems (HDS) helps organizations transform raw data into valuable information by making data more accessible and simpler to manage. As the leader in storage virtualization, only HDS offers a common, virtualized platform for all data and information.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"]\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive aligncenter wp-image-71 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/netapp.png" alt="netapp" width="46" height="52" />\r\n\r\n[/vc_column][vc_column width="3/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>NetApp</h3>\r\nNetApp creates innovative storage and data management solutions that accelerate business breakthroughs and deliver outstanding cost efficiency.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"]\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive aligncenter wp-image-72 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/oracle.png" alt="oracle" width="146" height="18" />\r\n\r\n[/vc_column][vc_column width="3/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Oracle</h3>\r\nKanatek has worked with Sun, acquired by Oracle, for over 20 years and have achieved numerous awards. Kanatek continues to work with Oracle as a gold partner.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"]\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive aligncenter wp-image-74 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/redhat.png" alt="redhat" width="138" height="44" />\r\n\r\n[/vc_column][vc_column width="3/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>RedHat</h3>\r\nRed Hat is one of the world''s leading provider of Linux® and open source technology. Kanatek helps bringing solutions into the mainstream with Red Hat by making high-quality, low-cost technology accessible to clients of all sizes.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"]\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive aligncenter wp-image-76 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/terix.png" alt="terix" width="99" height="39" />\r\n\r\n[/vc_column][vc_column width="3/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Terix</h3>\r\nTerix is a leading independent provider of flexible and innovative hardware and software maintenance service offerings. Kanatek partners with Terix to provide third party hardware maintenance.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"]\r\n\r\n<img class="img-responsive aligncenter wp-image-73 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/quantum.png" alt="quantum" width="143" height="24" />\r\n\r\n[/vc_column][vc_column width="3/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Quantum</h3>\r\nQuantum is the world''s largest supplier of tape drives, and its DLTtape technology is the standard for backup, archiving, and recovery of mission-critical data. In recent years, Quantum has been one of the pioneers in the emerging market of disk-based backup, offering a solution that emulates a tape library and is optimized for data protection.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]', 'Partners', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '426-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-30 22:06:11', '2015-04-30 22:06:11', '', 426, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/04/30/426-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
