r\n[person src="" name="Darryl Levesque" post="Director, Technology Solutions" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n\r\nAs the Director of Technology Solutions, Darryl brings a unique blend of expertise and experience to the table that helps him better understand customer needs. <a title="Darryl Levesque" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/darryl-levesque/">Read more...</a>\r\n\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="Michael De Cesare" post="Vice President, Finance and Human Resources" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n\r\nIn addition to managing the traditional functions within Human Resources and Finance, Michael spearheads the corporate financial reporting, treasury and budgeting functions. <a title="Michael De Cesare" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/michael-de-cesare/">Read more...</a>\r\n\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="David Kerrivan" post="Sr. Manager, Client Support and Managed Services" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n\r\nDavid, is responsible for the day-to-day strategic management of all services. His responsibilities include client support, project management, delivery and architectural services, as well as overall business planning. <a title="David Kerrivan" href="http://localhost/kanatek/about/david-kerrivan/">Read more...</a>\r\n\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Testimonials</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="8/12"][vc_accordion collapsible="1"][vc_accordion_tab title="Roy French, CIO, Saint Elizabeth Health Care"][vc_column_text]"Through Kanatek’s Managed Service offerings, we have reduced the complexity of our backup/restore processes while increasing reliability. Their approach has provided solutions that are sensitive to our unique requirements, allowing us to focus our IT resources on more strategic initiatives."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Luciana Pimentel, Project Manager, Torstar Corporation"][vc_column_text]"Kanatek have proven to be an extremely strong partner with deep capabilities in data protection. From the beginning, Kanatek understood the criticality of our infrastructure stabilization project. With a strong project manager and a flexible delivery team, I would recommend Kanatek as a company that has an excellent professional services staff."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="George Reichert, Chief Information Officer, Nortel Networks"][vc_column_text]"Kanatek''s backup and recovery managed services team provides Nortel with the needed resources and tools to ensure the availability of our data through cost-effective solutions and unparalleled support. Data is everything and Kanatek helps us ensure the availability of our valuable resources. You can rebuild the network or rebuild a server, but you cannot rebuild your data if you lose it."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Raj Kumar, Vendor Management, CIBC Mellon Trust Company"][vc_column_text]"I would like to compliment Kanatek for their service support. CIBC Mellon holds extremely high standards for vendors and Kanatek has consistently exceeded expectations in their proactive preparation, knowledge and response time. The Kanatek team has been attentive, patient, and committed to forging a strong partnership with our organization. I am confident that we can build on this relationship and look forward to continuing to work with Kanatek."[/vc_column_text][/vc_accordion_tab][vc_accordion_tab title="Wojciech Tryc, CTO, PIKA"][vc_column_text]"The Nuage agentless solution, in our view, dramatically enhance