(673, 1, '2015-05-02 12:30:57', '2015-05-02 12:30:57', '<img class="img-responsive alignnone wp-image-670 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/managed-services-banner.jpg" alt="managed-services-banner" width="940" height="400" />\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Kanatek’s market leading Managed Services offering ensures the full operation of an organization’s global Backup &amp; Recovery environment and includes:</h3>\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Monitoring and remediating backup integrity globally, 24x7[/list_item][list_item]Data recovery services in the event of a natural or man-made data loss[/list_item][list_item]Performing monthly restore audits and retention tests[/list_item][list_item]Participating in disaster recovery testing[/list_item][list_item]Managing Service Level Agreements (SLAs) and reporting on performance[/list_item][list_item]Identifying and implementing efficiencies and cost-saving processes[/list_item][list_item]Identifying opportunities to deploy new technology to further reduce costs[/list_item][list_item]Customizing reporting to each client’s needs[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\nKanatek Managed Services give clients the assurance that data is protected and accessible while allowing critical IT resources to focus on what makes the business unique.\r\n\r\n[button class="mybtn btn-orange" url="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/KTI-Managed-Services-2012.pdf" target="_blank"]Download Brochure[/button]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Managed Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '117-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-02 12:30:57', '2015-05-02 12:30:57', '', 117, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/05/02/117-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(674, 1, '2015-05-02 12:32:57', '2015-05-02 12:32:57', '<img class="img-responsive alignnone wp-image-667 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/backup-and-recovery-banner.jpg" alt="backup-and-recovery-banner" width="940" height="400" />\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Kanatek Backup &amp; Recovery Installation Services</h3>\r\nKanatek’s extensive experience in deploying Backup &amp; Recovery systems provides us with the knowledge and expertise to deliver archived and comprehensive solutions. Our Professional Services team provides end-to-end capabilities for designing, architecting, implementing and managing solutions to ensure that data is protected, archived and always available.\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Advantages of a properly installed, architected, or upgraded solution include:</h3>\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]<strong>Minimized Risk of Data Loss or Disruption</strong> - An effective Backup &amp; Recovery solution quickly restores file and application data in the event of system failure, data corruption or accidental deletion.[/list_item][list_item]<strong>Reduced Possibility of Data Loss or Disruptions during Implementation</strong> - Kanatek uses industry best practices to eliminate data loss or system disruptions during upgrades or implementation of Backup &amp; Recovery systems. By working with clients to prepare specific installation plans, the client’s staff enjoys uninterrupted access to their data.[/list_item][list_item]<strong>Decreased Operating Costs of Backup &amp; Recovery</strong> - Kanatek reduces a client’s time-to-value by providing subject matter experts and reducing the operating costs of Backup &amp; Recovery.[/list_item][list_item]<strong>The Best Technical Solution</strong> - Kanatek’s chosen software for data recovery enables optimized, efficient backups and faster restores of virtual environments through deep hypervisor integration. We manage both physical and virtual servers and multiple Backup &amp; Recovery products through one console.[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Backup and Recovery', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '227-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-02 12:32:57', '2015-05-02 12:32:57', '', 227, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/05/02/227-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(675, 1, '2015-05-02 12:34:53', '2015-05-02 12:34:53', '<img class="img-responsive alignnone wp-image-671 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/nuage-solutions-banner.jpg" alt="nuage-solutions-banner" width="940" height="400" />\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text css_animation=""]\r\n\r\nKanatek Nuage provides businesses that uses PaaS / SaaS based infrastructures such as Salesforce.com, Microsoft Dynamics, Google Apps or in Microsoft Azure, IBM Smartcloud, or Amazon S3 the ability to backup and restore large amounts of data in a really short time.\r\n\r\nWith a single interface for managing all backup data and complete storage hardware independent, the Nuage Cloud Backup V12:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Reduces your backup and recovery time[/list_item][list_item]Delivers high availability of data/applications[/list_item][list_item]Protect your IP[/list_item][list_item]Ensures regulatory compliance[/list_item][list_item]Ensure availability / recoverability of all your IP[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nDownload the Nuage Cloud Backup V12 product sheet:\r\n\r\n[button class="mybtn btn-orange" url="document.pdf" target="_blank"]Download[/button]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Cloud Solutions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '291-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-02 12:34:53', '2015-05-02 12:34:53', '', 291, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/05/02/291-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(676, 1, '2015-05-02 12:36:12', '2015-05-02 12:36:12', '<img class="img-responsive alignnone wp-image-669 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/disaster-recovery-banner.jpg" alt="disaster-recovery-banner" width="940" height="400" />\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Kanatek Recovery Services</h3>\r\nKanatek’s extensive experience in deploying Backup &amp; Recovery systems provides us with the expertise to design, architect, implement and manage solutions to ensure that data is protected, archived and always available. Our Data Recovery Service provides services to help you when data loss has occurred.\r\n\r\nEach Data recovery solution will be unique, based on your environment. Speak with our Solution Architects to plan the most expedient recovery of your data.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[box style="dark"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1>[text_color]Data Recovery Planning[/text_color]</h1>\r\n<h2>Your backup system must include a recovery plan</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/box]\r\n\r\n[vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Minimized the Risk of Data Loss or Disruption</h3>\r\nAn effective Backup &amp; Recovery solution quickly restores file and application data in the event of system failure, data corruption or accidental deletion. This can be a mission-critical issue for organizations. Analysis of the amount of downtime your organization can handle must be done in order to determine your DR planning approach. Kanatek uses industry best practices to eliminate data loss or system disruptions during upgrades or implementation of Backup &amp; Recovery systems.\r\n\r\nKanatek will help you:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Create, document and test a disaster recovery plan that is in line with your organization’s current high-level strategies.[/list_item][list_item]Quantify the cost of down-time to your organization and the cost of mitigating it.[/list_item][list_item]Perform disaster recovery in the event that you need assistance.[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Disaster Recovery', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '447-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-02 12:36:12', '2015-05-02 12:36:12', '', 447, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/05/02/447-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(677, 1, '2015-05-02 12:38:11', '2015-05-02 12:38:11', '<img class="img-responsive alignnone wp-image-672 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/support-services-banner.jpg" alt="support-services-banner" width="940" height="400" />\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Kanatek Client Support (KCS)</h3>\r\nMission-critical infrastructures need to be supported to protect organizations. Network failure, loss of data, or delayed access to data can all have a material effect on enterprises. Organizations protect their investments with tailored, 24x7 support contracts.\r\n\r\nKanatek Client Support is a 24x7 Data Management technical support service and provides unique value to clients. Here is what we do:\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Prevent escalation</h3>\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Immediate access to help desk[/list_item][list_item]Bilingual 24x7x365 support[/list_item][list_item]High resolution of issues without escalation (call closure rate ~95%)[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Deliver a Streamlined Support Experience</h3>\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]High depth of knowledge in your environment[/list_item][list_item]Ability to consolidate contract management[/list_item][list_item]Customized SLAs that can result in faster response times[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Multi-Vendor Support</h3>\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Kanatek has deep understanding of your heterogeneous IT environment[/list_item][list_item]Kanatek will resolve problems involving multiple vendors to deliver seamless and appropriate solutions and support[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Support', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '119-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-02 12:38:11', '2015-05-02 12:38:11', '', 119, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/05/02/119-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
