(695, 1, '2015-05-02 14:09:50', '2015-05-02 14:09:50', '<img class="img-responsive alignnone wp-image-667 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/backup-and-recovery-banner.jpg" alt="backup-and-recovery-banner" width="940" height="400" />\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Kanatek Backup &amp; Recovery Installation Services</h3>\r\nKanatek’s extensive experience in deploying Backup &amp; Recovery systems provides us with the knowledge and expertise to deliver archived and comprehensive solutions. Our Professional Services team provides end-to-end capabilities for designing, architecting, implementing and managing solutions to ensure that data is protected, archived and always available.\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Advantages of a properly installed, architected, or upgraded solution include:</h3>\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]<strong>Minimized Risk of Data Loss or Disruption</strong> - An effective Backup &amp; Recovery solution quickly restores file and application data in the event of system failure, data corruption or accidental deletion.[/list_item][list_item]<strong>Reduced Possibility of Data Loss or Disruptions during Implementation</strong> - Kanatek uses industry best practices to eliminate data loss or system disruptions during upgrades or implementation of Backup &amp; Recovery systems. By working with clients to prepare specific installation plans, the client’s staff enjoys uninterrupted access to their data.[/list_item][list_item]<strong>Decreased Operating Costs of Backup &amp; Recovery</strong> - Kanatek reduces a client’s time-to-value by providing subject matter experts and reducing the operating costs of Backup &amp; Recovery.[/list_item][list_item]<strong>The Best Technical Solution</strong> - Kanatek’s chosen software for data recovery enables optimized, efficient backups and faster restores of virtual environments through deep hypervisor integration. We manage both physical and virtual servers and multiple Backup &amp; Recovery products through one console.[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Backup and Recovery', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '227-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-02 14:09:50', '2015-05-02 14:09:50', '', 227, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/05/02/227-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(696, 1, '2015-05-02 14:10:55', '2015-05-02 14:10:55', '<img class="img-responsive alignnone wp-image-669 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/disaster-recovery-banner.jpg" alt="disaster-recovery-banner" width="940" height="400" />\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Kanatek Recovery Services</h3>\r\nKanatek’s extensive experience in deploying Backup &amp; Recovery systems provides us with the expertise to design, architect, implement and manage solutions to ensure that data is protected, archived and always available. Our Data Recovery Service provides services to help you when data loss has occurred.\r\n\r\nEach Data recovery solution will be unique, based on your environment. Speak with our Solution Architects to plan the most expedient recovery of your data.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[box style="dark"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1>[text_color]Data Recovery Planning[/text_color]</h1>\r\n<h2>Your backup system must include a recovery plan</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/box]\r\n\r\n[vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Minimized the Risk of Data Loss or Disruption</h3>\r\nAn effective Backup &amp; Recovery solution quickly restores file and application data in the event of system failure, data corruption or accidental deletion. This can be a mission-critical issue for organizations. Analysis of the amount of downtime your organization can handle must be done in order to determine your DR planning approach. Kanatek uses industry best practices to eliminate data loss or system disruptions during upgrades or implementation of Backup &amp; Recovery systems.\r\n\r\nKanatek will help you:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Create, document and test a disaster recovery plan that is in line with your organization’s current high-level strategies.[/list_item][list_item]Quantify the cost of down-time to your organization and the cost of mitigating it.[/list_item][list_item]Perform disaste