(701, 1, '2015-05-02 14:14:43', '2015-05-02 14:14:43', '<img class="img-responsive alignnone wp-image-672 size-full" src="http://localhost/kanatek/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/support-services-banner.jpg" alt="support-services-banner" width="940" height="400" />\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Kanatek Client Support (KCS)</h3>\r\nMission-critical infrastructures need to be supported to protect organizations. Network failure, loss of data, or delayed access to data can all have a material effect on enterprises. Organizations protect their investments with tailored, 24x7 support contracts.\r\n\r\nKanatek Client Support is a 24x7 Data Management technical support service and provides unique value to clients. Here is what we do:\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Prevent escalation</h3>\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Immediate access to help desk[/list_item][list_item]Bilingual 24x7x365 support[/list_item][list_item]High resolution of issues without escalation (call closure rate ~95%)[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Deliver a Streamlined Support Experience</h3>\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]High depth of knowledge in your environment[/list_item][list_item]Ability to consolidate contract management[/list_item][list_item]Customized SLAs that can result in faster response times[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Multi-Vendor Support</h3>\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Kanatek has deep understanding of your heterogeneous IT environment[/list_item][list_item]Kanatek will resolve problems involving multiple vendors to deliver seamless and appropriate solutions and support[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Support', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '119-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-02 14:14:43', '2015-05-02 14:14:43', '', 119, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/05/02/119-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(702, 1, '2015-05-02 14:16:55', '2015-05-02 14:16:55', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Why use a Kanatek Resident?</h3>\r\nIs your IT team short staffed? Is managing the protection of your data a part-time job, or allocated to a less experienced member of your team? Do you wish that you had a better understanding of your disaster recovery preparedness and your exposure to data loss?\r\n\r\nIf you answered yes to any of these questions, then you should be talking to a Kanatek Representative and discussing our NetBackup Residency Program.\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>What is a Kanatek Resident?</h3>\r\nThe Kanatek NetBackup Residency Program will augment your current IT Staff for short, or long term periods, using a highly qualified technical resident. The Kanatek resident is an experienced technical resource that has many years of experience in managing large scale backup environments, and they are specialists that are dedicated to managing your backup and recovery systems. We can provide seamless integration into your existing team of IT experts, while providing the NetBackup expertise beyond what might be available to you in-house.\r\n\r\nSome of the benefits:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Work side-by-side with internal staff, or work independently with minimal supervision[/list_item][list_item]Work on site or from an off-site location[/list_item][list_item]Manage the day-to-day backup/recovery operations[/list_item][list_item]Implement Best Practices for backup &amp; recovery[/list_item][list_item]Troubleshoot backup &amp; recovery issues and raise trouble tickets if required[/list_item][list_item]Perform upgrades, new installations, or the decommissioning of backup clients[/list_item][list_item]Implement new backup features and functionality[/list_item][list_item]Report to Senior Management on a regular basis[/list_item][list_item]Assist senior staff with determining long term data protection strategies[/list_item][list_item]Assist with Disaster Recovery planning, exercises and execution[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\nFor more information on our residency program, contact Kanatek at <a href="mailto:info@kanatek.com">info@kanatek.com</a>.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Residency', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '468-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-02 14:16:55', '2015-05-02 14:16:55', '', 468, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/05/02/468-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(703, 1, '2015-05-02 14:17:38', '2015-05-02 14:17:38', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Obsolete infrastructure in your data centre is a problem</h3>\r\nIn the data centre, old infrastructure like servers and routers costs your organization money and space. These inefficiencies can cost you:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Higher maintenance costs.[/list_item][list_item]Higher power consumption.[/list_item][list_item]Valuable physical space.[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\nIf you throw it away, you can open up sensitive data still remaining to theft and illegal use, data such as financial information or personal employee or customer information. Even if the data has been removed, improper wiping can leave behind valuable or sensitive information.\r\n\r\nDiscarding electronic equipment in landfills or improperly recycling them also causes environmental damage by leaking heavy metals into the ground or nearby water systems. Poorly discarded infrastructure can usually be traced back to your organization through serial numbers, in turn leading to public relations issues and possibly heavy penalties.\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Turn to Kanatek for Responsible and Ethical Decommissioning</h3>\r\nKanatek’s Decommissioning Service helps you safely identify, remove and destroy obsolete infrastructure by offering end-to-end management and customized coordination of the destruction process that:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Identifies the right candidates for decommissioning[/list_item][list_item]Reduces the overhead costs incurred by old gear[/list_item][list_item]Is environmentally responsible[/list_item][list_item]Ensures data security without compromise[/list_item][list_item]Safeguards your organization’s reputation[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\nKanatek partners with Artex Environmental to ensure that decommissioned servers and other hardware are securely and ethically destroyed. Artex is a certified primary processor with the Ontario Electronic Stewardship (OES) and is certified under the National Environmental Recycling Standard 2010 as well as ISO 14001.\r\n\r\n[spacer height="25px"]\r\n<h3>Three great reasons to choose the Kanatek Decommissioning Service to solve your obsolete infrastructure problem:</h3>\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Protect your data and protect your reputation.[/list_item][list_item]Work collaboratively with you to determine your business and IT needs and determine the right approach.[/list_item][list_item]Manage the entire project from end-to-end.[/list_item][/list_arrow]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Decommissioning', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '472-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-02 14:17:38', '2015-05-02 14:17:38', '', 472, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/05/02/472-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(704, 1, '2015-05-02 14:18:29', '2015-05-02 14:18:29', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Gain powerful, actionable insight into the state of your IT infrastructure</h3>\r\nKanatek can help you define an approach to investing in and implementing IT infrastructure components, linking your IT strategy to your corporate objectives.\r\n\r\nKanatek will identify opportunities for increased efficiency, business value and growth, working with you to develop business cases and roadmaps with clearly-defined steps to help you determine exactly how to get where you''re going, quickly and always aligned to your business objectives.\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Strategize and design the best solution to meet your business needs through professional storage and backup/recovery assessments[/list_item][list_item]Design and deploy the right infrastructure using technologies from industry-leaders[/list_item][list_item]Constantly identify and improve operational efficiencies[/list_item][list_item]Streamline and manage your environment by reducing interfaces, data sources, changes and backup tools to lower risk, improve throughput, and reduce costs[/list_item][list_item]Support your IT environment through highly qualified, certified, multi-vendor support teams[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\nContact us at <a href="mailto:info@kanatek.com">info@kanatek.com</a> for more information on how Kanatek can help streamline your organization''s data infrastructure.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Assess', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '495-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-02 14:18:29', '2015-05-02 14:18:29', '', 495, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/05/02/495-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(705, 1, '2015-05-02 14:19:58', '2015-05-02 14:19:58', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Enhance the efficiency of your backup and recovery software, hardware assets, and IT resources</h3>\r\nKanatek''s Professional Services team can implement reliable solutions that offer:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Guaranteed data backups[/list_item][list_item]Data recoverability[/list_item][list_item]Reduced impact on your business[/list_item][list_item]Minimal system downtime[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\nKanatek answers the need for enterprise backup control and rationalization with solutions that deliver a single, centralized point of control for managing backup, from the desktop to the server.\r\n\r\nWith over 30 years of technical experience with Symantec and Oracle products, the Kanatek team provides first class implementations and customized upgrades - tailoring and optimizing solutions to fit your organization''s needs.\r\n\r\nContact us at <a href="mailto:info@kanatek.com">info@kanatek.com</a> for more information on how Kanatek can help deploy your backup solutions.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Integrate', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '497-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-02 14:19:58', '2015-05-02 14:19:58', '', 497, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/05/02/497-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(706, 1, '2015-05-02 14:20:33', '2015-05-02 14:20:33', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Reduce costs. Find efficiencies. Provide ROI.</h3>\r\nWe manage your existing data backup operations environment with experienced resources, while providing remote management services.\r\n\r\nPredictable, business-focused IT services:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]<strong>Kanatek Residency Program</strong> - Engage an on-site, experienced Kanatek Resident to help manage your daily backup and operations - gaining access to best practices, leading-edge technologies, and expertise beyond what might be available in-house.[/list_item][list_item]<strong>Backup &amp; Recovery Services</strong> - The Kanatek Managed Services team is focused on managing your data backup and recovery operations, while leveraging your investment in facilities and infrastructure. Your data stays on site, except where it is backed up remotely, and remains within your control at all times. We provide the expertise to ensure backups are done, 24x7; assuring your data assets are protected and risks are mitigated.[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\nContact us at <a href="mailto:info@kanatek.com">info@kanatek.com</a> for more information.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Manage', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '499-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-02 14:20:33', '2015-05-02 14:20:33', '', 499, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/05/02/499-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(707, 1, '2015-05-02 14:21:01', '2015-05-02 14:21:01', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3>Save time. Prevent escalation. Alleviate stress.</h3>\r\nKanatek''s unparalleled offering of customer support services allows you to take advantage of our Professional Services Team''s technical expertise and over 30 years of experience with partner products:\r\n\r\n[list_arrow][list_item]Kanatek Client Support for Software and Hardware Maintenance[/list_item][list_item]Help Desk for Support and Ticket Management[/list_item][list_item]Immediate access to help desk, with no dispatch interface[/list_item][list_item]Single point contact with 24x7x365 availability[/list_item][list_item]Bilingual support[/list_item][list_item]Vendor Management and Liaison[/list_item][/list_arrow][spacer height="25px"]\r\n\r\n<strong>Symantec’s Authorized Technical Assistance Partner Program</strong> (TAPP) helps Kanatek deliver value added services to our clients with increasingly complex IT environments. As a trusted advocate with priority access to Symantec’s advanced-level technical assistance staff, we can offer our clients greater levels of technical assistance with a broader range of value-added services. The TAPP program allows our clients to depending on our skilled certified bilingual team of experts to manage and maintain their Backup Exec backup problems.\r\n\r\nContact us at <a href="mailto:info@kanatek.com">info@kanatek.com</a> for more information.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Support', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '501-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-02 14:21:01', '2015-05-02 14:21:01', '', 501, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/05/02/501-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
